4. Monitor the QueueProcessor Lambda function via the AWS console (CloudWatch) and observe for errors.
5. Access the backend database to confirm the door open and close events are recorded.

Acceptance Criteria:
- All 2,000 load test simulation devices return an OK status in the script output.
